{"tid":1475184,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[八一八] 民陣和理非回合","createTime":"2019-08-15T11:37:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T12:24:39.000Z","uid":16934,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"33ec743d7a894503b004c86a2853f52d14eef305","tid":1475184,"uid":16934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T11:37:48.000Z","msg":"雖然今次表明係和理非回合 麻煩大家記得<span style=\"color: red;\">gear照帶</span>但唔洗上 相信大家都有眼睇到而家班狗已經係癲晒 失晒控 帶gear唔係為左衝 係為左保護自己同手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而且萬一班狗又發癲 起碼都有裝可以對抗下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次班狗唔批遊行都預左 亦預左大家一定會繼續行落去 當中實有鬼起衝突 希望大家冷靜d記得初衷<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不分化 不割蓆 現場要討論清楚 唔好為捉而捉 緊記鬼永遠都捉唔晒</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r7dGixU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr7dGixU.jpg&h=8bddc089&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FnCsd6F.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFnCsd6F.png&h=2fa551a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span><br />\n<br />\n小弟有d事今次去唔到 希望大家加油同小心 行埋我果份<br />\n<br />\n天佑香港🇭🇰 希望有一日可以同你慶祝勝利"},{"pid":"5068545a553be61612cc0459f1231fa4156c44ee","tid":1475184,"uid":32187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T11:39:53.000Z","msg":"基本法賦予既又被打壓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f99a17950aeeed8216bb631e9851478b36dc882","tid":1475184,"uid":39205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T11:40:43.000Z","msg":"反警黑嘅遊行要黑警批係咩玩法<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1475107\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1475107</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"af6a105a47d7d40afc824fe0cc4f9e4e30125e07","tid":1475184,"uid":16934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5068545a553be61612cc0459f1231fa4156c44ee","tid":1475184,"uid":32187,"like"